This is a detailed summary of the **DC-8 (Delta Charlie 8) Walkthrough** to serve as comprehensive notes for your OSCP preparation. The process is broken down into the standard penetration testing phases, including the specific tools and commands demonstrated in the video.

***

## ⚠️ Important OSCP Exam Note

The instructor explicitly notes that **SQLMap is NOT permitted** in the OSCP exam. Any SQL Injection must be performed **manually**. The tool was used in the video *for demonstration and efficiency*. Be sure your manual SQLi skills are up to par!

